Classes

class  INetworkReachableNodesCommandImp
 FdoINetworkReachableNodesCommand subclasses from FdoINetworkCommand and is the interface that defines the FDO network reachable nodes analysis feature. An instance can be created through the FdoIConnection::CreateCommand method. Not all FDO providers will support this command. The FdoICommandCapability should be used to verify if a given provider support this command. More...
